{"tid":1008792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：眾多外國領事中，唯獨英國領事最睇唔起香港人，最賤","createTime":"2019-02-04T17:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T11:44:58.000Z","uid":133680,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"42e797c95a0f64f483d1bf5a8256232ab7d10002","tid":1008792,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T17:24:02.000Z","msg":"陳雲：我轉貼了多國駐港總領事的賀年片段，唯獨未有轉貼英國駐港總領事在2月2日發表的片段。因為他在拍片之後向觀眾告別，說要返回領事館工作了，衣着也是打工仔那種地產經紀小子look。<br />\n總領事是代表國家的。他賤，雖然他努力在講廣東話。他將英國王室的貴族格局、將歷代香港總督的儒雅格局變成香港打工仔那種賤。英女王將這種人派來香港，是看不起香港人，覺得香港人周身賤格。"},{"pid":"bd535f123e1db31f989f5c0901935dee896fc818","tid":1008792,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T17:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e78a9aafca56277ca3e16cb5a2025f900db214","tid":1008792,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T17:31:28.000Z","msg":"From舊登：云伯今年又賣淘寶貨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4XVxMMH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4XVxMMH.png&h=e0966e37&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4N87AE3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4N87AE3.png&h=20798a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rFRtj6K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrFRtj6K.png&h=4fe893e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qf6AKyr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqf6AKyr.png&h=c9a8a189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7015030&amp;type=CA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D7015030%26type%3DCA&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ79ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=9e0f7720\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7015030&amp;type=CA</a>"},{"pid":"763bb56268c345e936617cb6a8c33a41